AU  -  NCT02078687,
TI  -  Growth, Risks of Allergy and Metabolic Syndrome in 6 Year Old Children Born Preterm Compared to Postdischarge Nutrition
JA  -  https://clinicaltrials.gov/show/NCT02078687
PY  -  2014
C3  -  CTgov NCT02078687
M3  -  Trial registry record
KW  -  Birth Weight
KW  -  Hypersensitivity
