TI  -  In a placebo-controlled 36-week phase 2 trial, treatment with MGL-3196 compared to placebo results in significant reductions in hepatic fat (MRI-PDFF), liver enzymes, fibrosis biomarkers, atherogenic lipids, and improvement in NASH on serial liver biopsy
JA  -  Hepatology (Baltimore, Md.)
PY  -  2018
