s by NAT2 phenotype in this ad hoc analysis, the LAT1 inhibitor nanvuranlat further improved its clinical efficacy and safety in the NAT2 NR population. Therefore, selecting NAT2 NR for nanvuranlat treatment may improve the risk ‐benefit ratio. Clinical trial information: UMIN000034080.
