TI  -  ACHIEVEMENT OF LOW DISEASE ACTIVITY OVER 52 WEEKS IN PATIENTS WITH ACTIVE AXIAL SPONDYLOARTHRITIS ON BIMEKIZUMAB TREATMENT: RESULTS FROM THE PHASE 3 STUDIES BE MOBILE 1 AND BE MOBILE 2
