TI  -  POS0864 ACHIEVEMENT OF REMISSION DEFINED BY ABSENCE OF OBJECTIVE SIGNS OF INFLAMMATION VERSUS ASDAS INACTIVE DISEASE IN PATIENTS WITH ACTIVE AXIAL SPONDYLOARTHRITIS TREATED WITH BIMEKIZUMAB: 52-WEEK RESULTS FROM TWO PHASE 3 STUDIES
