TI  -  Achieving Increasingly Stringent Clinical Response Criteria &amp; Lower Levels of Disease Activity Is Associated with Greater Improvements in Physical Function &amp; HRQoL in Patients with Active Axial Spondyloarthritis: 16-Week Results from Two Phase 3 Randomized, Placebo-Controlled Studies
