TI  -  IMPACT OF BIMEKIZUMAB ON MRI INFLAMMATORY AND STRUCTURAL LESIONS IN THE SACROILIAC JOINTS OF PATIENTS WITH AXIAL SPONDYLOARTHRITIS: 52-WEEK RESULTS AND POST HOC ANALYSES FROM THE BE MOBILE 1 AND 2 PHASE 3 STUDIES
