TI  -  IXEKIZUMAB IMPROVES SIGNS, SYMPTOMS, and QUALITY of LIFE in PATIENTS with AXIAL SPA IRRESPECTIVE of DISEASE DURATION: RESULTS from the COAST-V, COAST-W and COAST-X TRIALS
