TI  -  HOW QUICKLY WILL I FEEL BETTERWITH THIS NEW DRUG?-RAPIDITYOF TREATMENT RESPONSE IN PATIENTS WITH AXIAL SPONDYLOARTHRITIS TREATED WITH BIMEKIZUMAB: ANALYSIS FROM 2 PHASE 3 STUDIES
