TI  -  POS0788 BIMEKIZUMAB DEMONSTRATED SUSTAINED EFFICACY AND SAFETY ACROSS THE FULL SPECTRUM OF AXIAL SPONDYLOARTHRITIS: 3-YEAR RESULTS FROM TWO PHASE 3 STUDIES AND THEIR OPEN-LABEL EXTENSION
