TI  -  Spondyloarthritis research consortium of canada (SPARCC) baseline MRI SI joint score ≥2 better predicts response to golimumab than does assessment of spondyloarthritis international society (ASAS) MRI positivity in nonradiographic axial spondyloarthritis
